videoSnippet.title: Lotus Chess Arena - lichess.org
videoSnippet.description:
https://lichess.org/tournament/nG8gqJv2
Hello Everyone!
Join us for an exciting chess tournament sponsored by Lotus Chess (www.lotus-chess.com/).
Test your skills, compete against strong opponents, and may the best win!

1st Prize – 6-month subscription to Lotus Chess
2nd Prize – 3-month subscription to Lotus Chess
3rd Prize – 3-month subscription to Lotus Chess
4th Prize – 3-month subscription to Lotus Chess
5th Prize – 3-month subscription to Lotus Chess
6th Prize – 3-month subscription to Lotus Chess

As usual, I will be streaming and showcasing your games.
Enjoy :)
